entities.createSql: CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` (`id` TEXT NOT NULL, `booth` TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, `name` TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, `summary` TEXT, `links` TEXT NOT NULL, `store` TEXT, `catalog` TEXT, `favorite` INTEGER NOT NULL, `ignored` INTEGER NOT NULL, `notes` TEXT, `seriesInferredSerialized` TEXT NOT NULL, `seriesInferredSearchable` TEXT NOT NULL, `seriesConfirmedSerialized` TEXT NOT NULL, `seriesConfirmedSearchable` TEXT NOT NULL, `merchInferred` TEXT NOT NULL, `merchConfirmed` TEXT NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY(`id`))

CREATE VIRTUAL TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `${TABLE_NAME}` USING FTS4(`id` TEXT NOT NULL, `booth` TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, `name` TEXT NOT NULL COLLATE NOCASE, `summary` TEXT, `links` TEXT NOT NULL, `store` TEXT, `catalog` TEXT, `favorite` INTEGER NOT NULL, `ignored` INTEGER NOT NULL, `notes` TEXT, `seriesInferredSerialized` TEXT NOT NULL, `seriesInferredSearchable` TEXT NOT NULL, `seriesConfirmedSerialized` TEXT NOT NULL, `seriesConfirmedSearchable` TEXT NOT NULL, `merchInferred` TEXT NOT NULL, `merchConfirmed` TEXT NOT NULL, content=`artist_entries`)
contentSyncTriggers: CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_artist_entries_fts_BEFORE_UPDATE BEFORE UPDATE ON `artist_entries` BEGIN DELETE FROM `artist_entries_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END
CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_artist_entries_fts_BEFORE_DELETE BEFORE DELETE ON `artist_entries` BEGIN DELETE FROM `artist_entries_fts` WHERE `docid`=OLD.`rowid`; END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_artist_entries_fts_AFTER_UPDATE AFTER UPDATE ON `artist_entries` BEGIN INSERT INTO `artist_entries_fts`(`docid`, `id`, `booth`, `name`, `summary`, `links`, `store`, `catalog`, `favorite`, `ignored`, `notes`, `seriesInferredSerialized`, `seriesInferredSearchable`, `seriesConfirmedSerialized`, `seriesConfirmedSearchable`, `merchInferred`, `merchConfirmed`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`id`, NEW.`booth`, NEW.`name`, NEW.`summary`, NEW.`links`, NEW.`store`, NEW.`catalog`, NEW.`favorite`, NEW.`ignored`, NEW.`notes`, NEW.`seriesInferredSerialized`, NEW.`seriesInferredSearchable`, NEW.`seriesConfirmedSerialized`, NEW.`seriesConfirmedSearchable`, NEW.`merchInferred`, NEW.`merchConfirmed`); END

CREATE TRIGGER IF NOT EXISTS room_fts_content_sync_artist_entries_fts_AFTER_INSERT AFTER INSERT ON `artist_entries` BEGIN INSERT INTO `artist_entries_fts`(`docid`, `id`, `booth`, `name`, `summary`, `links`, `store`, `catalog`, `favorite`, `ignored`, `notes`, `seriesInferredSerialized`, `seriesInferredSearchable`, `seriesConfirmedSerialized`, `seriesConfirmedSearchable`, `merchInferred`, `merchConfirmed`) VALUES (NEW.`rowid`, NEW.`id`, NEW.`booth`, NEW.`name`, NEW.`summary`, NEW.`links`, NEW.`store`, NEW.`catalog`, NEW.`favorite`, NEW.`ignored`, NEW.`notes`, NEW.`seriesInferredSerialized`, NEW.`seriesInferredSearchable`, NEW.`seriesConfirmedSerialized`, NEW.`seriesConfirmedSearchable`, NEW.`merchInferred`, NEW.`merchConfirmed`); END
